README.md
     1‚Üí# dotenv
     5‚ÜíDotenv is a zero-dependency module that loads environment variables from a `.env` file into [`process.env`](https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/process.html#process_process_env). Storing configuration in the environment separate from code is based on [The Twelve-Factor App](https://12factor.net/config) methodology.
     6‚Üí
     7‚Üí[Watch the tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YtkZR0NFd1g)
     8‚Üí
     9‚Üí&nbsp;
    10‚Üí
    11‚Üí## Usage
    13‚ÜíInstall it.
    14‚Üí
