   587‚Üí### Config ‚Ä¶
   605‚Üí#### Options ‚Ä¶
   607‚Üí##### path
   609‚ÜíDefault: `path.resolve(process.cwd(), '.env')`
   610‚Üí
   611‚ÜíSpecify a custom path if your file containing environment variables is located elsewhere.
   612‚Üí
   613‚Üí```js
   614‚Üírequire('dotenv').config({ path: '/custom/path/to/.env' })
   615‚Üí```
   616‚Üí
